  "body": [
    [
      {
        "type": "config",
        "directions": "Select each card to learn important details about art exhibits."
      },
      {
        "type": "flipCard",
        "cards": [
          {
            "height": "370px",
            "width": "250px",
            "front": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "<strong>What is an art exhibit?</strong>"
              },
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "flipimg_01",
                "width": "100%",
                "alt": "three people smiling and looking at framed art on a wall",
                "src": "interactives/flipcard_08_01_03/intmedia/p3_img1.jpg"
              }
            ],
            "back": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "An art exhibit is a way for artists to put their artwork on display in a public place. Exhibits give people in the community a chance to enjoy art."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "height": "370px",
            "width": "250px",
            "front": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "<strong>Who are exhibits for?</strong>"
              },
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "flipimg_02",
                "width": "100%",
                "alt": "a woman and a young girl pointing at art and talking",
                "src": "interactives/flipcard_08_01_03/intmedia/p3_img2.jpg"
              }
            ],
            "back": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Professional artists, students, and members of the community can all participate in art exhibits and have their work on display."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "height": "370px",
            "width": "250px",
            "front": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "<strong>Where do art exhibits take place?</strong>"
              },
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "flipimg_03",
                "width": "100%",
                "alt": "an outdoor art exhibit",
                "src": "interactives/flipcard_08_01_03/intmedia/p3_img3.jpg"
              }
            ],
            "back": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "There are many different places for art exhibits. They are often found at schools, libraries, art galleries, festivals, parks, and county fairs."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "type": "flipCard",
        "cards": [
          {
            "height": "370px",
            "width": "250px",
            "front": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "<strong>When do art exhibits take place?</strong>"
              },
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "flipimg_04",
                "width": "100%",
                "alt": "three people looking at art and taking photos",
                "src": "interactives/flipcard_08_01_03/intmedia/p3_img4.jpg"
              }
            ],
            "back": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Art exhibits are taking place all the time! They occur many different times throughout the year."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "height": "370px",
            "width": "250px",
            "front": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "<strong>Why are exhibits important for the community?</strong>"
              },
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "flipimg_05",
                "width": "100%",
                "alt": "a woman talking to two people about a piece of art on display",
                "src": "interactives/flipcard_08_01_03/intmedia/p3_img5.jpg"
              }
            ],
            "back": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Art exhibits give people in the community a chance to enjoy art. The artist gets the chance to learn, grow, and share a special message or idea with the community."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "height": "370px",
            "width": "250px",
            "front": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "<strong>How can an artist get their work in an exhibit?</strong>"
              },
              {
                "type": "image",
                "id": "flipimg_06",
                "width": "100%",
                "alt": "a small group of people discussing a sculpture",
                "src": "interactives/flipcard_08_01_03/intmedia/p3_img6.jpg"
              }
            ],
            "back": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "Once you find an art exhibit to join, see if there are any guidelines. Select a work of art you are proud of and want to share with others."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  ]
}